oardgamemechanic":1,"boardgameexpansion":1,"boardgameversion":5,"expandsboardgame":0,"boardgameintegration":0,"contains":0,"containedin":2,"reimplementation":2,"reimplements":0,"boardgamefamily":2,"videogamebg":0,"boardgamesubdomain":1,"boardgameaccessory":0,"cardset":1},"secondarynamescount":0,"alternatenamescount":5,"primaryname":{"nameid":"1580541","name":"Dirty Pig","sortindex":"1","primaryname":"1","translit":"Dirty Pig"},"alternatenames":[{"nameid":"588660","name":"Drecksau"},{"nameid":"686935","name":"Moddervarkens"},{"nameid":"703705","name":"Γουρουνάκια στη λάσπη"},{"nameid":"1206097","name":"髒小豬"},{"nameid":"2334439","name":"드렉사우 딜럭스"}],"description":"<p>Only a dirty pig is a happy pig!</p>\n\n<p>In <em><strong>Dirty Pig</strong></em>, first released as <em>Drecksau</em>, each player has 2-4 clean pigs in front of him and three cards in hand. Each turn one card is played. By playing a &quot;Dirty Your Pig&quot; card, one pig can be sent into the mud. One of the pig cards in front of you is flipped over to show a dirty pig on the back. Rain cards clean all pigs, even your own! Barn cards protect your pigs from the rain, while lightning cards destroy the barns &ndash; but lightning rod cards protect barns from lightning cards. Farmer cards are played to dirty someone else's pigs: the farmer likes clean pigs... Pigs in a barn that are protected with a barn door are safe from the farmer. A pig in a barn, with a door, and a lightning rod, is completely protected! The first player who dirties all of his pigs wins!</p>\n\n<p>Note that while <em>Drecksau</em> has a maximum player count of four, <em>Dirty Pig</em> contains additional cards that allow for play with up to six.</p>\n\n","wiki":"<p><strong><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.boardgamegeek.com/microbadge/26629\" onclick=\"window.open(this.href, '_blank'); return false;\">Microbadges</a></strong></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/microbadge/26629\"><img alt='Microbadge: Drecksau fan' onmouseover=\"return overlib('Drecksau fan', WRAP );\" onmouseout=\"return nd();\" title=''class='mbimg'loading=\"lazy\"src=\"https://cf.geekdo-static.com/mbs/mb_26629_0.png\"></a> Drecksau fan</p>\n\n","website":{"url":false},"imageid":"4598767","images":{"thumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/TOddi3WhObt77hb63vseDg__small/img/nr3ASpVF-vAg3SkAdLoQROJJSDE=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic4598767.jpg","micro":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/TOddi3WhObt77hb63vseDg__micro/img/Xbjt7W4lIHJb-piIUQFH6By514E=/fit-in/64x64/filters:strip_icc()/pic4598767.jpg","square":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/TOddi3WhObt77hb63vseDg__square/img/ZjQNlabfKhfQQzvLjVf6hX8beHI=/75x75/filters:strip_icc()/pic4598767.jpg","tallthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/TOddi3WhObt77hb63vseDg__tallthumb/img/UkqW5LRzoaW69nAejDxWQ08m4AY=/fit-in/75x125/filters:strip_icc()/pic4598767.jpg","previewthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/TOddi3WhObt77hb63vseDg__previewthumb/img/emdQFJNfbuBx7C2yw1TX5PoLX2I=/fit-in/300x320/filters:strip_icc()/pic4598767.jpg","square200":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/TOddi3WhObt77hb63vseDg__square200/img/8Q3NnBP5oMgNBOeZtJUNIlw5VbM=/200x200/filters:strip_icc()/pic4598767.jpg","original":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/TOddi3WhObt77hb63vseDg__original/img/TAy_xrKBOo54VRrzNKrOt9hT4KY=/0x0/filters:format(jpeg)/pic4598767.jpg"},"imagepagehref":"/image/4598767/dirty-pig","imageurl":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/TOddi3WhObt77hb63vseDg__itemrep/img/jZ2Kn8c8X9lW5eopOabaWlXjPW8=/fit-in/246x300/filters:strip_icc()/pic4598767.jpg","topimageurl":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/jNsX1EB92xCOAxFlIYPPSA__itemheader/img/tT3EMlHl8jRZJEBCLzgOtrf8-bc=/800x450/filters:quality(30):strip_icc()/pic1473321.jpg","imageSets":{"square100":{"src":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/TOddi3WhObt77hb63vseDg__square100/img/WjOtkFiQ54eQaglmkOzubUc2DAM=/313x0:873x560/100x100/filters:strip_icc()/pic4598767.jpg","src@2x":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/TOddi3WhObt77hb63vseDg__square100@2x/img/T9YVymepc5w4N0z_PEqQc4YH_VQ=/313x0:873x560/200x200/filters:strip_